data.description: Well maintained one-level home in the Meador Park neighborhood with lots of extras. 25x25 two story workshop with power and ac located in the backyard. Custom deck with gazebo attached to house. Privacy fenced backyard with gates on both sides of house. Ceiling fans in all three bedrooms, sun room, and family room. Master bedroom has remote controlled fan and lighting. Vivint security system with outdoor cameras, camera doorbell, door sensors, and wall control panel as well as a smart thermostat. Custom woodworking detail throughout the home. 2 door fridge/freezer included with the sale. Updated main bathroom with new fixtures. New carpet throughout. Come see this unique property before it's gone...
